videos.description: On the fast break, Iowa State's Matt Thomas leaves the defender with no hope when he lobs the ball up to Jameel McKay who finishes with the big slam dunk.
videos.headline: Four-on-one ends with alley-oop dunk for Iowa State

videos.description: Iowa's Jarrod Uthoff quiets Hilton Coliseum with a loud dunk over the defender with authority.

videos.description: Monte Morris' jumper with eight seconds left puts Iowa State up for good for the first time since trailing by 20 points to stun arch-rival Iowa 82-81.
videos.headline: Iowa State completes incredible comeback over Iowa

videos.description: Iowa State F Jameel McKay describes what it feels like to beat Iowa 83-82 and breaks down how his team was able to come back in the second half.
videos.headline: Jameel McKay: 'Hilton Magic is the only magic I believe in'

videos.description: Iowa State G Monte Morris breaks down the last few seconds that led to his team's 83-82 victory over Iowa and says he is pleased with his team's big win.
videos.headline: Monte Morris elated over last-second win over Iowa
